modName: MMOxReview's Alexstrasza - Beautiful Nord Woman - Genuine MxR Save
summary: This is not exactly a mod, it is one of MxR's earliest saves, but with an updated and current Alexstrasza. Now you can finally play as her! ApachiiSkyHair is neccesary.
descriptionHtml:
[img]http://s13.postimg.org/rifjg5rg5/maxresdefault2.png[/img]This is not exactly a mod, it is one of [b]MxR[/b]'s earliest saves, but with an updated and current[b] Alexstrasza[/b]. Now you can finally play as her!

[b]ApachiiSkyHair is neccesary.

[/b]Have fun, and credit goes to [b]MMOxReview[/b] for creating this amazing character.
Check out his incredible [b]channel[/b] on [b]youtube[/b], and if you love Skyrim mods, you shouldÂ definitely subscribe.

I recommend you use the [b]Familiar Faces [/b]mod, which will allow you to have [b]Alexsztrasza[/b] as a follower
or an enemy on one of your own saves.
